item.title: CVE-2023-40530|2024-08-02T18:38:49.295Z -- skylark%20holdings%20co.%2C%20ltd. -- %27skylark%27%20app%20for%20android
item.description: Improper authorization in handler for custom URL scheme issue in 'Skylark' App for Android 6.2.13 and earlier and 'Skylark' App for iOS 6.2.13 and earlier allows an attacker to lead a user to access an arbitrary website via another application installed on the user's device.
